headline: Atmus Filtration Technologies (NYSE:ATMU) Delivers Impressive Q3 CY2025
summary: Filtration products manufacturer Atmus Filtration Technologies (NYSE:ATMU) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 10.9% year on year to $447.7 million. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.69 per share was 15.1% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
